    <summary>Unofficial, community-maintained Chocolatey package for the Aircall Workspace desktop app (may lag official releases).</summary>
    <releaseNotes><![CDATA[
  ### Aircall Workspace 1.13.10

  - Updated package to Aircall Workspace version 1.13.10.
  - Official Aircall release notes: https://support.aircall.io/en-gb/sections/29441424037405
  ]]></releaseNotes>
    <description><![CDATA[
## Unofficial / Community package (not maintained by Aircall)
This Chocolatey package is **unofficial** and **community-provided**. It is **not** published or maintained by Aircall.
It may **lag behind** Aircall's officially released desktop versions.

## What this package does
- Installs the Aircall Workspace desktop application for Windows.
- Downloads the installer from Aircall's official download endpoint.

## Support / expectations
For Aircall product support and official release notes, please refer to Aircall's official channels.
For issues with this Chocolatey package (install/uninstall scripts, packaging, version lag), please use the package issue tracker linked in this nuspec.
]]></description>
  </metadata>
  <files>
